title: The main title in Tibetan
role:
possible values:
- author
- translator
- pandita
- sponsor (of translation)
- scribe
- translator2 (when two translations are indicated in the colophon)
- pandita2
- revisor
- revisorpandita
- revisionsponsor
- revisor2
- revisor2pandita
- revisor3
- revisor3pandita
- translationplace
- revisionplace

Important note: translator2 is not just another translator who worked with the first translator, it's someone who reworked the translation at a later date, and thus didn't work with the initial translator
identification: the ID of the identified person in the "Persons" sheet (this column is what Bruno did)
indicated value: The name as indicated in the colophon
identification 2: this is something the librarians did some time ago
sources: possible values are IDs from the source spreadsheet, "colophon" or "karchak"
